     #svn_opt_revision_date.<br>  *         If no error occurred, return #SVN_NO_ERROR.  *  * @since New in 1.5.  *  * @see #svn_depth_t<br> #svn_client_ctx_t<br> @ref clnt_revisions for  *      a discussion of operative and peg revisions.  */
